♪ Too shy, shy ♪

19:41.160 --> 19:42.960
♪ Hush, hush, eye to eye... ♪

20:46.920 --> 20:47.840
Thank you.

22:45.680 --> 22:46.520
Stefan?

22:47.520 --> 22:49.320
Um, tea.

22:52.480 --> 22:55.520
Er, look, I'm going to go to the pub
for some lunch.

22:55.760 --> 22:59.440
- If you fancy tagging along.
- No. I'm alright.

23:01.160 --> 23:05.680
- You didn't have any breakfast.
- Dad, I'm fine.

23:07.640 --> 23:09.160
Is everything alright?

23:15.560 --> 23:18.840
Stefan, I'm worried about you.
You've been stuck in your room for weeks.

